Module passwordmanager
Package passwordmanager.backend.local.livetesting

Class EntryGenerator

java.lang.Object
passwordmanager.backend.local.livetesting.EntryGenerator
public class EntryGenerator extends Object
The EntryGenerator class is responsible for generating random Entry objects for testing purposes within a password manager application. This class provides a method to generate a specified number of random Entry objects using pre-defined arrays of titles, emails, passwords, usernames, links, and categories.

The generated entries are randomly selected from the predefined arrays for each attribute, ensuring variety in the generated data. Timestamps for creation and modification are not included in the generation process and will be set by the caller if needed.
